{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MS01_010.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh no, thank you. You were most helpful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hello Monika, Sir Julio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "What were you two doing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I was having a sword match with Sir Julio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "A match?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "After fighting together, I noticed that Monika has splendid swordplay. I asked her if she would spar with me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "After actually sparring with her, I can see that Monika's use of her shield is quite skillful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...However, most people who use quick sword movements such as yourself tend to evade rather than use a shield."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Why did you decide to use a shield?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I'd be fine without one alone, but when I'm fighting alongside everyone, sometimes there's little room to move."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I figured that having a shield for those times would offer better protection."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Why do you choose not to use a shield?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "In my case, there's a part of me who doesn't like using shields, but I also stress offensive power."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "If you use a sword that's too light, your attacks may not deal significant damage to certain larger opponents."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "This sword also makes blocking attacks much easier."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "True, a sword that large would probably work well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Exactly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Huh. It sounds like swords are pretty complicated."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That's right. I need to improve my skills even more. Sir Julio, would you mind sparring with me again sometime?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Of course. You're more than welcome anytime."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I'll just keep working on my alchemy."
        }
    ]
}